Publish to Wordpress Plasmoid
----------------------------
This is a plasmoid that allows you to write blog posts directly to your wordpress blog without entering the actual wordpress blogs website.

Depends on:
 * PyKDE / PyQT
 * Wordpress XML-RPC Library by Michelle Ferretti (http://code.google.com/p/wordpress-library/). (Included in Project. Please let me know if this is considered unethical/illegal).

NEWS:
 2009-07-23:
  First release! Uploading to your blog works.

